{"title":"农民的歌","authors":["朱子奇"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":3,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳听黄牛叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳听黄牛叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕来到了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨树柳树绿芽冒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树下小牛满地跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛儿快喂饱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁儿快擦好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕运动大展开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全村农民哈哈笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳听黄牛叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫人多勤劳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸扶犁出村去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥送粪上地了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈把米淘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来把火烧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参加生产人人忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里村外好热闹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花喜鹊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月里，好天气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花喜鹊儿忙报喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一报报到我家里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庆祝平津得解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟弟举手敬个礼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家大小笑嘻嘻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大姊姊，来提议，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二姊和我也同意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产支前为胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取模范多努力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花喜鹊，劳驾你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请把消息捎到别家去。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}